Baby I trust you my friend
I think Azuki just dumped me.
She found out that I have been hiding what happened between her mom and my uncle...
and told me she could not trust me.
Unlike Miyoshi, Azuki is not the type to forgive cheating.
W-Well, yeah... but this is bad.
Yeah, for now, I would better apologize.
But I have not done anything wrong, so please trust me.
Well, um, if you trust me, I should not have to tell you...
If no one's done anything wrong, you should be able to talk about it.
I can only think you are covering for Takagi.
But when you were worried about doing that photo book, you hid it from me.
I think hiding something to avoid worrying others
and hiding something you did wrong are two different things.
But I already told you I did not do anything wrong!
How come you get to decide?
If nothing's wrong, you should be able to tell me.
You do not trust me enough to tell me!
In the end, neither Azuki nor Miyoshi trusts us.
Even though we have not done anything wrong.
If Saiko and Azuki break up because of something I did...
Let us just tell them everything!
First, I will stop exchanging ideas with Aoki.
I will tell her afterwards and promise never to do it again.
And that thing with Iwase was just a misunderstanding.
If there is nothing left to hide, then you and Azuki can make up.
You are the only man I can trust right now,
so honestly, I enjoy talking with you.
This is the first time I have been able to be honest and talk freely with a man.
I look forward to continuing our relationship as manga authors and occasional rivals.
I could not tell her I wanted to stop talking with her.
Well, she did not do anything wrong.
Should you tell just Azuki everything?
And if I tell her not to, she will just get even angrier.
Let us just wait it out and see how it goes for a while.
But I have caused trouble for both of you...
If they apologize, then we can tell them everything.
Otherwise, they will walk all over us in the future!
Now, let us get started on that serialization storyboard for when Tanto gets first place!
Saiko's really stubborn when it comes to things like this.
No luck with either Takagi or Mashiro.
Miho and Mashiro had a fight?
I cannot believe he would hide something from me.
Miho's stubborn when it comes to things like this...
It usually comes on release day...
An email from Azuki about her impressions.
Hey, how about you stop being stubborn and tell Azuki everything?
I will not be the one to fold first.
Anyways, let us get to the office.
It is going to be a while before we find out NEXT's final rankings...
I should have asked him to tell us the early results.
Tanto... can get first place, right?
It is not can, it is will.
I think it will go over well with little kids,
but NEXT has a higher readership age than Jack does.
Saiko, you are just useless without Azuki's It was great!
Tanto took 1st place in the final rankings!
This is the first time we have gotten 1st place!
It is the first time one of my edited works has gotten 1st, too, idiot!
Let us ride this momentum all the way to the next serialization meeting!
I did not know I would be this happy about getting 1st in the final rankings.
Next time, let us get 1st in Jack!
I think it did well, considering it was up against Ashirogi.
2nd is just fine for getting serialized.
It did not get to have the first few pages in color, after all.
I wonder if that is all it was?
Time of Blue Leaves did well with older males and females.
That was pretty much what we were aiming for.
It is been a while since I have seen a romance like this.
Yeah, if we do something about the art.
So that was the issue, after all.
If Aoki is fine with drawing the faces alone,
you could try pairing her up with Nakai Takuro again, with him as the artist and her as the author.
This time, in the magazine itself.
I will keep pushing her to pair up with Nakai.
I will not lose to Tanto lying down!
If it goes well, it could get a drama adaptation!
She could have said Congratulations, at least...
Maybe she is working really late?
I guess she will not reply unless I apologize.
Do not you think she is taking things too far?
You do not mind if I congratulate you, right?
I am glad that Ashirogi, whom I collaborated with, was number one.
Let us both work hard from here on out.
Why am I so happy even though I only got second place?
No, I cannot feel that way for him.
This may be sudden, but we decided to try out Time of Blue Leaves as a one-shot in Jack!
If we can have Nakai do the art.
The general consensus in the editing department is that it would be for the best.
Nakai and a fellow female assistant?
So I do not think you need to worry about him anymore.
I do not have the right to criticize Nakai now.
If it will improve the manga, I will trust you and do as you say.
Then I will follow up with Nakai immediately.
I will speak with him directly.
Um, what was it you wanted to talk about?
I was wondering if you would draw for me again.
Time of Blue Leaves, which was published in NEXT...
is going to be tried out as a one-shot in Jack.
I did not think it was possible, but could that character in Time of Blue Leaves really have been...
My editor suggested that you should do the art.
I will be brief, since I slipped out of work to come talk to you.
You see, I am enjoying my current job, and I am getting along well with Katou Natsumi, a fellow assistant.
I am having trouble deciding between you two.
If you want to work with me, go out with me.
Dating as a requirement for working together?
As a man... as a person... you are awful!
Since you have gone this far, my doubts have all been cleared up.
Natsumi is waiting for me, so...
For the first chapter, we will go with The gum that makes you say cool stuff
and The cast that punches back.
Which of these inventions do you want to use for chapters two and up?
He has not sent Azuki any mail since then.
We have to get this serialized, make it into a big hit, and then we will get an anime...
I cannot even email her until then?
Actually, is our promise to get married once I get an anime even valid at this point?
I will go home for today and think about it.
Here is the list of inventions.
Number them in the order of which ones you like most.
If he is like that, it will affect our work.
This is not the time to be stubborn.
Even though you have finally come to visit, you have been looking down this whole time.
I am sorry for staying over so long.
It is like I have more daughters now;
Your friend... is it a boy?
Hey, what is going on with Miho and Mashiro?
She does not tell me anything,
so give me the details before she gets back from work!
I need to go make a call.
The one that used Miho and Mashiro's romance!
What are you doing, telling everybody about it?!
You are so obviously prattling away with both Iwase and that female manga author!
Are the two of you going on group dates with both of them every day, or something?
Even though you never take me out on a proper date,
you are really chummy with pretty girls!
You should only do stuff like that after you break up with me
I cannot stand that Azuki and Mashiro ended up like this because of us.
I feel the same way, but...
It is because of you, not because of us.
Anyways, I am going to explain it to you, so just calm down and listen.
I cannot get Nakai to do the art now.
I am telling you, it was a misunderstanding!
I told Iwase I liked you 1,000 times more than her.
And how much more do you like me than Aoki?
Why are you being realistic there?
But since it is realistic, I will believe you when you say you like me.
Yeah, I like you more than anyone.
If you are going that far, then take me out on a date to the zoo.
Then I will explain everything properly at the zoo.
Hmm, so you are really going to make it up to me by taking me out on a fun date?
If I am not satisfied, I will beat the crap out of you.
That will be up to you.
But I really do like you more than anyone.
See you at 3 at the monkey mountain, then.
Let us see... monkey mountain, monkey mountain.
I hope I can tell Miyoshi apart from the monkeys.
No, she is not capable of that...
At this time of all times.
I do not know what to do!
Wait a minute, I feel like I am forgetting something.
You did not have to go this far to show off to me!
How can you say that when you were all over him, you temptress!
She was not all over me!
I just had my hand on her shoulder!
You should have just kissed while you were at it!
That is what you wanted me to see, right?!
I hope you are happy together!
I love you more than anyone else!
You are just trying to keep hold of me by copying Mashiro.
I am 19, and you are still 18!
But we are still college students!
I think it is a wonderful thing for college students to marry.
Who the hell are you, anyway?
I thought he was cheating with Iwase.
I was serialized in Shounen Jack under the name Aoki Kou.
but you two were hugging back there.
Since you drew a manga like that, you and Takagi must be real close, huh?
No, we just talked about manga!
There is a really good explanation for that...
No, I do not have a reasonable justification for hugging you.
Would you really meet at the zoo by coincidence twice?
And on top of that, Aoki was troubled both times?
I will not call him anymore, and I will not talk to him if we meet by coincidence again.
So trust Takagi and marry him!
He proposed on a whim just to stop me from running off.
No, if you say yes, then I will do it.
If we are always together, there will not be any more misunderstandings like this.
I would have preferred to do it after becoming a famous manga author,
but if you are willing to struggle with me, then...
I think it is wonderful for people to struggle together and form a strong bond.
You guys say some nice things.
B-But there is stuff like the ceremony and my parents' permission to worry about...
I have to ask for your hand in marriage and stuff.
Do you think I would get permission?
I mean, I will do my best!
Then let us get married when you get serialized.
But you will be busy when that happens, so we will just get registered.
We will have a ceremony when we can.
Please let me know when that happens.
I will support you from behind.
I just said I would not talk with Takagi anymore...
But Takagi's the only man you can trust and consult, right?
I have never had a person I could get along with like Takagi.
I think I was starting to like him.
Why did you have to be so honest about that?
You should have stuck with the We are just fellow manga authors story.
But Takai and Nakai are both idiots.
If I were a man, I would definitely choose you.
I can still change my mind...
What are you saying in front of the girl you just proposed to?!
I will think less of you!
No, that was just one of his jokes.
Aoki, please continue talking to Takagi.
In exchange, I want you to become friends with me, too!
Um, well, I was just wondering if Azuki will be satisfied with this.
I cannot trust you, but I can trust Aoki.
That was a joke, too... right?
If I do not apologize, our relationship might end like this!
But Azuki should trust me more...
This might be a break-up email!
If it was going to come to this, I should have...
If anyone saw this, they would think Who does this guy think he is?
He is got three beautiful girls around him.
He is picking on you, Miho.
I should tell him the four of us are having tea.
He will get even more confused.
Even though he said he was headed home for today.
What are you doing leaving me out?
But you are mailing each other again, right?
Because of you, I was forced to agree to marry Miyoshi when we get serialized.
What do you mean by forced?!
Let us get serialized for sure and make a popular manga!
When it gets an anime, you get married, too!
I will work hard and aim for a serialization.
We are going to get married!
Is there anyone who will lend me a hand in accomplishing my dream?
